/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the street below. The street itself is lined with trees and lampposts, adding a touch of greenery to the urban landscape. Power lines crisscross above, forming a network of lines against the blue sky. In the distance, buildings rise, their silhouettes forming a cityscape against the sky. The sun shines brightly, casting a warm glow over the scene. The image is taken from a low angle, making the viewer feel as if they are standing at the edge of the street, looking down at the city below.
